{"tid":1304803,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【全民皆兵】1 8 區全民體能訓練， 有冇得諗？","createTime":"2019-07-10T16:54:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T11:45:18.000Z","uid":123115,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e0a6da7be9e437b32b1fceb40b910690130ddd59","tid":1304803,"uid":123115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:54:48.000Z","msg":"香港冇軍事訓練 好多時都好輸蝕<br />\n其實今次好多時大家都會輸體能 <br />\n特別係長期缺乏鍛練嘅學生， 絲打 同埋打工仔<br />\n<br />\n有冇各區專業巴絲 （e.g. 軍時訓練/ PT）可以每朝/ 每星期 定期喺自己果區啲公園 搞下training <br />\n<br />\n一來可以光復公園 <br />\n二來大家強身健體 <br />\n三來保護自己保護家園  （對長期抗爭好有用）<br />\n<br />\n不限男女 有心都可以自己參加<br />\n有冇固定trainer 都唔緊要 但training 時間要長期同固定<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得有冇得諗？<br />\n<br />\n利申： 想參加 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9cef6fa1f8a1435b6ad66654415471177d4898e","tid":1304803,"uid":123115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:54:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b34689a09a8094d533c4b9fccd152fc12aa4984","tid":1304803,"uid":123115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:55:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"61d1115bc2d8c797bd38802571c279509a27d8b8","tid":1304803,"uid":123115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:56:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"365428f0aff080a9b4512593bda775bbd68c026e","tid":1304803,"uid":123115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:56:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"21d7800fcbf7488d691fffb903b359c496b38f98","tid":1304803,"uid":123115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:57:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9697f6043d0684e614668b87bb320f63aa771648","tid":1304803,"uid":260181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:57:45.000Z","msg":"有呀，全民運動group<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1303234/page/1\" dat